<br>
Unfortunately it is the whiners and complainers that make the most noise, but believe me when I say that everybody there was impressed by the way that you lead an unbelievable number of players on that Vox raid.  Discipline was great although there seems to be problems that may never be solved: pushing giants through walls (didn't happen this time), and keeping Vox in her lair.  <br>
<br>
There were MANY people on that raid who had never been on a dragon raid, or never been on a Vox raid.  4 out of 6 people in my group were first-timers.  Your patience and ability to deal with all the problems this creates for raid leadership is simply amazing.<br>
<br>
Thank you again for another great SB/CoG victory.<br>
